snippet.title: Super Burger Master
snippet.description:
You will be overwhelmed by the crazy fast food kitchen work. You have to write down the customer's needs and make the perfect food to get the highest tip from the customer, but don't let the fast food restaurant go out of business.

GAME FEATURES
First make the fried chicken, coat the chicken with various sauces, place the chicken in the deep fryer and cook it to perfection.
Then stack the ingredients, choose from a variety of breads, and create delicious sandwiches piled high with fried meats, cheeses, toppings, and sauces.
To create a delicious drink at the end, add the juice to the glass and mix the flavors together for an energizing and delicious drink.


MORE FEATURES 
. Easy and addictive gameplay
. Upgrade for more fun
. Satisfy different customers!
. Exquisite graphic style
. No wifi needed. You could play it anywhere.
